short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Import products from different warehouses and many more

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Shopify users who wish to dropship products from different sites can use this extension.
Using this extension, Shopify users can import products from aliexpress site and others and sell without maintaining any inventory stock.

Please note you need to have shopify subscription before using this extension. to read about user data and permission policy, check at 
https://dsmatepro.com/about_extension.html
